Assert length of bottlenecks is greater than or equal to 0

Let formatted_bottlenecks be format bottlenecks as bottlenecks
Assert length of formatted_bottlenecks is greater than 0

Call print bottlenecks as bottlenecks

Note: Test memory usage
:End Note
Let frames_for_memory be extract stack frames
Let memory_usage be get memory usage of frames_for_memory
Assert length of memory_usage is greater than 0

